quran[22{c,v,t}:
54,28,Wa nabbi'hum annal maaa'a qismatum bainahum kullu shirbim muhtadar
54,29,Fanaadaw saahibahum fata'aataa fa'aqar
54,30,Fakaifa kaana 'azaabee wa nuzur
54,31,Innaaa arsalnaa 'alaihim saihatanw waahidatan fakaano kahasheemil muhtazir
54,32,Wa laqad yassarnal quraana liz zikri fahal mim muddakir
54,33,Kazzabat qawmu lootim binnuzur
54,34,Innaa arsalnaa 'alaihim haasiban illaaa aala Loot najjainaahum bisahar
54,35,Ni'matam min 'indinaa; kazaalika najzee man shakar
54,36,Wa laqad anzarahum batshatanaa fatamaaraw binnuzur
54,37,Wa laqad raawadoohu 'andaifee fatamasnaaa a'yunahum fazooqoo 'azaabee wa nuzur
54,38,Wa laqad sabbahahum bukratan 'azaabum mustaqirr
54,39,Fazooqoo 'azaabee wa nuzur
54,40,Wa laqad yassarnal Quraana liz zikri fahal mim muddakir
54,41,Wa laqad jaaa'a Aala Fir'awnan nuzur
54,42,Kazzaboo bi Aayaatinaa kullihaa fa akhaznaahum akhza 'azeezim muqtadir
54,43,Akuffaarukum khairum min ulaaa'ikum am lakum baraaa'atun fiz Zubur
54,44,Am yaqooloona nahnu jamee'um muntasir
54,45,Sa yuhzamul jam'u wa yuwalloonad dubur
54,46,Balis Saa'atu maw'iduhum was Saa'atu adhaa wa amarr
54,47,Innal mujrimeena fee dalaalinw wa su'ur
54,48,Yawma yushaboona fin Naari'alaa wujoohimim zooqoo massa saqar
54,49,Innaa kulla shai'in khalaqnaahu biqadar
